src.main
Drivers for offline radiative transfer computation, routines shared by all rt packages 1D & 3D

-- files --
exoplanet_mod.F90           - limited options, 1d hook-up
input.F90                   - 1d input
main.F90                    - 1d driver
output.F90                  - 1d output

exo_radiation_cam_intr.F90  - shared interface for operation with CAM
exo_radiation_mod.F90       - shared two stream radiative transfer solver
rayleigh_data.F90 	    - shared rayleigh scattering parameters
mcica.F90                   - shared monte carlo independent cloud approximation
mcica_random_numbers.F90    - shared mcica routines
